N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 701.11 - Transfer of case

State Regulations

In the absence, disability or disqualification of a hearing
officer or for other good cause, a case assigned to a hearing officer may be
transferred to another hearing officer by the Commissioner. Notes
